{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "For most of twenty twenty-five, AI engineers were yelling at each other.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0d559d55c52cc9bc5b6c8fcb37be649cae047000825c0d85028a9c6fbe5d9bc4",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "One side: just give the agent a shell. The other: use M C P, the protocol Anthropic shipped last November.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c080975c30f0f5cb26759059992d5b589c9713617c2bb5a9a3ce6b838a7d798",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Both sides ran benchmarks. Both sides had screenshots.",
      "checksum": "sha256:24928cf332922f19d79bf6d30b093145149b31d37755540c93623ea1bec100e1",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Both were arguing about the wrong thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0a3779c24bac52537d455657edb926f605b205ec37eb41c089e586bfe79be309",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 40
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "We probed seven real M C P servers ourselves.",
      "checksum": "sha256:325ba98e4ccb907e49e48ad8d9c4ab5d1e9bbdb5d0fa98050a884bdba0a1dfd0",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 47
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Sixteen thousand tokens of schema sitting in the model's prompt before the agent does anything useful.",
      "checksum": "sha256:85d5518b07bd3720422b9f59c2af9f190077eb1a699f5d4a84e0273518a355bc",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "In the next eight minutes you'll see the one move that took the same workflow from one hundred and fifty thousand tokens down to two thousand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09be3c4a735b421258033d789ed35f4a759b6e3a3626ecdbab04d415c5dcfe99",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 8.498503401360544,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Where the debate actually came from. And what to do about it on your own machine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2b0e0fcfb7c4d6e3b9b4372024bfb43b9814735daf54e06c5a1e6a43b5c81997",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Let's go. This is where it started. In November twenty twenty-four, Anthropic published the Model Context Protocol \u2014 a standard way for agents to talk to external tools.",
      "checksum": "sha256:13a78a041a2955dd3623cd025ca68393ec4817b1befc216fbdfcfb4ad5e90810",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 11.052698412698414,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 114
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Within twelve months, two camps had formed. The M C P camp pushed typed contracts, O auth, audit trails, multi tenant safety.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7ef138efc742bcc984058d47322ea00dd2ccd9451e24235387929b1f786fb27d",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 8.777142857142858,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The C L I camp said the protocol was paying tax on knowledge the model already had.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0a9f47188b4851f9326f1ebf643709ede7bee82c84fd75a1f272185aa4a9791f",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 164
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The fights looked like they were about M C P versus C L I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4073f7706606bbb79ca9e211f2ebc60f3cb5010d309d8298d26ea66a658d09c9",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 181
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "They weren't. They were about how tool definitions get loaded into the model's context window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:91ed890380bc9e6640058e86edce574ab7e15f6dce09291d9bc85bd3840ca0bf",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 6.222947845804988,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 195
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "That distinction is the whole story. Here's what each side actually measured. The C L I camp ran the numbers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83fa1fc190a67be07d6f07934d0a0196caa9a13f8f813e7c312d6a5b1ca0a72c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 7.291065759637188,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 210
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Playwright's M C P server eats around fifteen thousand tokens of schema before it does anything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:63560b9c2cf4a19cbcd3cbbb6a1fe0625d3a69722eb8e1258bdfd33ac614a53b",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 230
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Chrome DevTools eats about seventeen thousand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:624e87096379e01bc6652488a1b1be353dcb3706ecb9095247ce0378b95c440f",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 246
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "A typical multi server setup burns fifty thousand tokens of context before the agent runs its first command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:61493ee83ef6dde3ebe636f1483c9f45269a0412b4fb73aed93fbc9ecc677a46",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 252
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "We reproduced this on this machine. Seven real M C P servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:604d92511bf14a3ed9b7abe853cee45defa821feb0e045c7ab1e1227dc7bc304",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "One hundred and one tools. Sixteen thousand five hundred tokens of pure schema, sitting in the model's prompt at session start.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07fb970d985fb3fb9ebde5547aebd1d595a7f3abdbc4636164148aabf4ba61bc",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 8.17342403628118,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 282
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Now the M C P camp's side. C L I agents break on multi tenant apps because there's no shared state.",
      "checksum": "sha256:255c469477898d41976a29395e2e23a78e19aa1e202aa48f47ac9906634e3a27",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 6.408707482993197,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 303
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "There are no typed contracts, so the agent guesses at output shapes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f9f5e2f4a48ea2939cb08491b2ad734eb3f6a986e99b1067b9414612f11e9fd",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 324
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "On unfamiliar APIs, agents waste turns parsing raw H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07670f2dbddccbe524e94883131c1eb361bd84654c3d629b726a1b73d1e3c565",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 336
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "IBM showed an agent reverse engineering Next dot J S internals just to read a webpage.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b758e06b4628c538478cb68a2c43217211f674508693d07df379a76df40358dc",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 348
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "We ran that experiment too. Plain curl on a single page app returns one thousand seven hundred tokens of empty H T M L \u2014 no rendered content.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1414eb9710d36b9accfaf93fdbcba93571d28fed3ab540082fe6f1a156fa3975",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 11.145578231292516,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 364
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "A Playwright M C P server, with a real headless browser, returns one thousand eight hundred and eighty nine tokens \u2014 the full page.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bfdb8f25de280e050bc8ef011943456177dcc1146cada324a86db6f94c254d6",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 8.591383219954649,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 392
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Both sides had receipts. Both arguments were real.",
      "checksum": "sha256:16e035d4b9a8ae74488b2479f230fc8e1a08d174d1ba866b46763f88f6ff5367",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 416
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "So which one wins? Neither. That was the wrong question.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c047267940e8011e4643bcf6724d8baa5d7dacf516dc2f1610f174d83113f37c",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 424
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Here's the move that resolved it. On November fourth, twenty twenty-five, Anthropic published an article called Code Execution with M C P.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a9009c2f7f2a6c69f5dd07208afaebc2a2dd5a05da21078e337f2a656217efa7",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 434
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Their example was simple. Pull a Google Drive transcript.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6d6b3f1801261281bd015377ab0ac7546db8abeaccafc8e595bfbb26ee62c17b",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 456
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Push a summary to Salesforce. The old way, with both tool schemas eagerly loaded and the transcript piping through the model on every step, burned one hundred and fifty thousand tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3864fca9624308ad7f739c15147723aa554bef9ab1e14bb62360dae34beac382",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 11.517097505668934,
      "word_count": 31,
      "words_offset": 465
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "The new way, a few lines of TypeScript that import only what they need, burned two thousand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:feacb27a986ac1fe26c3ca1c0615d4d15798ee830439b35b3915cbbd93459777",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 496
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "A ninety eight point seven percent drop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c902b5c196821e25d0db476e005cdfb8beac9217b5646079e685a7e521e2b8e",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 513
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Three months later, Cloudflare took it further.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0aa8a7f09b5c753c6d0f276018dda93e16a536a566841dc4dfea0755b4614ae0",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 520
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "They exposed their entire two thousand five hundred endpoint A P I through M C P \u2014 using just two functions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ecd04ee5a8b6efb700bbbde30660bf973267adecf2c7a2329384063d43b79337",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 6.873106575963718,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 527
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Search, and execute. The traditional version would have consumed one point one seven million tokens of schema.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a139d563aa6e6aaf431ee277392af862c9bca4edd1708fdaefdeb9edab64088c",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 6.919546485260771,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 548
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "The new version: about one thousand. Ninety nine point nine percent reduction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9901078aaa2dad4c6086e1c29b07b489dbcee0c8348929f56f5690327b1d7cec",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 565
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "The fix wasn't a different protocol. The fix was a different binding.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b6b4ea90d616c760161871a1e080db6689d7ac2e458d83b81d4d0f322d985929",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 577
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Tool definitions stopped living in the model's context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:753df71d2eab832e517241a7666c2444070e5796a936439045495f0301f5b784",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 589
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "They moved to the filesystem. So what is Code Mode, in plain language?",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ecb5e9a9289f0c65a8fce3ec0d9e50cb53c8d5ecea1182017d6150ba4a30011",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 597
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "The model writes code. The code calls tools.",
      "checksum": "sha256:700266cfe9864be08060f87798a992785a9ee412bd1d1ef8c4a958cc078a2627",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 610
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "The tools live on disk. Five layers, top down.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fb0c25bb4528cb2378bc5f30a985c62b049b671550b48aaf927bf50e309275a7",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 618
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "The agent on top, picks the right primitive per task.",
      "checksum": "sha256:43293016188a2ffcc4b0fe1688fa9b30f2a3293049e8e032b4a331704783e43f",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 627
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Below it, the runtime executes that code in a sandbox.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bdd70ae68737a1d654291ff4d2357cc97ef9056992ef9d70d3ad0e4010a79940",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 637
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Underneath the runtime, bash gives you everything already on your path \u2014 git, curl, grep, ffmpeg.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4decf2d5b688cdb7048b17fac9eefd53a6a3abce205758938c7053a27cd34a3",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 6.873106575963718,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 647
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "The model has seen these in training. No schema needed. Beside bash, typed module imports give you the proprietary APIs \u2014 Stripe, Salesforce, your internal services.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db8c3cecc4d8cdf75ec7afe8cda9339e7fa761c4c0579e1eec2ec12195adb978",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 10.448979591836734,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 663
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Each tool is a small TypeScript file. The type signature travels with the import.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5056f22e22aea503a54a3d8a3b87df52028915d9466a2fb4900ce31eae1e134",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 689
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Tool definitions enter context only on the import line.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6f3ba73b0b71cf1e4fdba35a77a4d349cc9fe2e36444b14eb768d49481a58d38",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 703
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "Every other tool stays out. And underneath all of it, M C P still sits there \u2014 for the cases where you actually need multi tenant O auth, runtime tool discovery, or audit trails.",
      "checksum": "sha256:902751cb85c6989ccb8d3bda88a0ab444ac2f67415f66392f434b724458ab7f8",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 12.027936507936507,
      "word_count": 34,
      "words_offset": 712
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Picture it. Three lines. Import search files from at tools slash github.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5919cbf2a281c6a86f04e70f58acb6029c2b69cd0a6c5642caf5ccdff47d131",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 746
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "Import send message from at tools slash slack.",
      "checksum": "sha256:66d2232e279056e518b01bfe8bd597c5fd2ea3b00474f8b6d3c51bb51028e195",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 758
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "Two function calls. The Github and Slack tool definitions enter the prompt only on the import lines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0ac2a8891299818a00a5082bcf54aee5e837967a6faf0b3d840a0409c4f0eb16",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 766
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Every other tool in the catalog stays out.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56e3e6ae0e7a346f6e24d6c6e7b1f967879dcbd2fbf716db28568ecd33025799",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 783
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "M C P's typed contracts, plus C L I's lazy loading, in one runtime.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8a8a17c4730df35e0a62c390ca0d013e41e1f993b536475bdeb4c4aa36bc1d0b",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 791
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "You'll see takes online that M C P is dying.",
      "checksum": "sha256:32e2f64afd062123115e4145adee570ddb0f241112964ab9db2cce3074ab623e",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 805
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "They're wrong. Anthropic just reported ninety seven million monthly S D K downloads.",
      "checksum": "sha256:491a84c1584b6290dce28c474d4679d909487d909aca9e7e11614a2149ea0e83",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 815
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "Over ten thousand active public M C P servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:18530e75b9bbb3a7818b81e4d163dbfe69a832e542296120619325cbc26f323a",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 828
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "Seventy five plus Claude connectors built on it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d4dfe4dc746b7c9a883967e57b6c06dcd08b099eaa3ccc5fe38c68424e4c1d96",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 837
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "This is the fastest growing piece of agent infrastructure right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bc8fc612158638daa21218422502b15c8b04c0dece436b554dba03f288431956",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 845
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "The verified sources are right there. Anthropic's Code Execution article from November fourth, twenty twenty-five.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0deac24f2be15489d82bcf5db629fa9b0a42cdd3e84082d6389dce53abcdc940",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 856
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "Cloudflare's Code Mode post from February twentieth, twenty twenty-six.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a1544ba205cf954f6e92f49dd263f098f2d17f92f2b0c2d15be98b16c89af87d",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 871
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Anthropic's own Agent Skills documentation, which ships the same idea inside Claude \u2014 three level progressive disclosure.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9796c3ec654e06c2e8f33cd9b328551b1cd6aeae6611757f88b4728effae2470",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 7.848344671201814,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 880
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "Just the frontmatter loads by default, about thirty to fifty tokens per skill.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f47fff6f6229f8dd35291745a1955ff579b2191ded42f598497ee53d00a4220a",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 897
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "The full instructions only load when the skill is relevant.",
      "checksum": "sha256:02e6a214dc0bf1a7b796f6089105823d1f12a7da35c7e2934e6acc8d85b2069c",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 910
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "Linked files only when the skill body references them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:000fdb8a190d2c340438b923f721594903ee744d1f29cdc09ee2a53c6dc13dd8",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 920
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "That's Code Mode for the agent on your laptop, today, no extra infrastructure.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5293c7af5a62b5703ed86388289292b765c5c098fa8a79838c847b452d262101",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 929
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "What died was the assumption that you load every tool upfront.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f69ef0f0fef7419ba3c6a4c5473a069bc58d9d93fa3a3616a4b5579aaad7cbe7",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 942
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "It's also true that some companies are stepping back.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2c78603902f95120d22de8d07ae512aa37d30c6f5d86211a43af5ba669700201",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 953
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "In March twenty twenty-six, Perplexity moved away from M C P for their flagship Agent A P I, citing context bloat and authentication friction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1bb8fecac27d906088901c53f5747cba914382ba59a9b12c1cc7cf15d8ad5096",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 9.520181405895691,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 962
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "They kept their M C P server for third party developers though.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f86f79ba5e96535065a0b57f90f1eb44a5e0080aeb6414120acf0e82ec27aa4c",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 986
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "They dropped it for their own product because their use case is single agent, known tools, predictable workflows.",
      "checksum": "sha256:55b4a86ad57a0599214bc65bfb509fa6a73ae2f56889ee866351368463fb4d46",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 998
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "That's the opposite of where M C P shines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c7b3299eb12dac279d7e219fb4ef318ae2d95ba348bfbef37d8861522fb64a74",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1016
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "So what do you do about all this in your own setup?",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e30229e8ec7a970baa10af5c97a95e1d33723ae8942cc89b305040049c2297b",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1025
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "Three rules. If a binary on your path already does the job, use bash.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5baac7994a65b616d697f239f78c8632e4a77fac8950c3fa60ed12b34a1a6265",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1037
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "It's free. The model knows it. If you're calling a proprietary A P I, write a typed module import the agent can pull in on demand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6731b3e9dfbea5b29e178d0a10d93a1144050d2beeb57a896db5f2b908298db8",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 1051
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "If you genuinely need runtime tool discovery, multi tenant auth, or governance, use M C P \u2014 but expose it through a search and execute pattern like Cloudflare did.",
      "checksum": "sha256:abe51c8c1793c3892fac44c941e14d63d1b77f2a5323480463b0a256dc30c060",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 10.077460317460318,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 1077
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "Don't load the full schema at session start.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b73c17c0174a7f0230f37da27264d9fc70e8d6fb412f882d26f47a0349fdf10d",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1106
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "Two things nobody on either side has solved cleanly yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a9dc596f31080c6a770e509d43cb1c45fb45140b155e5b5abbdb6439c9a6aae6",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1114
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "Cross server composition. Cloudflare's pattern works beautifully for one A P I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1d2880e89b6160232fb8d5837e7da073d7fcc2f05321f9bcf3ccbd68ebdf21dd",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1124
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "If your agent needs to compose five different services, you're back in context pressure territory unless every one ships as a code import.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c39ae451e7d1ced7f1606b5298a1bfcd0636ea1d3a3f2ed76f217506862a8318",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 7.987664399092971,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 1136
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "And discoverability. With M C P, the agent gets the menu of available tools for free at session start.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db61456d0922318267f4cf8e4c10de393ae38f3c165a9bf3419c06d87237f6b1",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 6.130068027210885,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 1159
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "With Code Mode, the agent has to know which imports exist.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7fffb9badbba3710a54810b7319ea9e1a91477af8a5a5511afae585d66d5ef4e",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1178
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "Anthropic Skills solves it through filesystem layout.",
      "checksum": "sha256:84fd0a93a2cb8d781c854120994b13042918082ecb544ac84011aee7993a06d3",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1189
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "Cursor and Cline solve it differently. There's no standard yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f29ba93963d6d01762c1dbf9a8155f156a387fdc94ea36f7c3e0e3b9ce2d3d13",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1196
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "And the tradeoff isn't free. Code Mode moves the cost from the context window to the sandbox.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b42d71c735f0eee5c177c1543b6c4f584d08148edca5050d927508c503794f1d",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 1206
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "For a developer running Claude Code locally, that cost is negligible \u2014 it's your machine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e497522bf43cedb90d3231aa3c72ebd799a4c4d000cda9bb71c81fe3f72f31de",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 1223
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "For an enterprise running thousands of agents, it's a real engineering line item.",
      "checksum": "sha256:640c27b0db5c2784afbe6ed4f3a13c93132f143fbfe3d67df73f4525b1cfbdb6",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1238
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "Here's the takeaway. M C P versus C L I was the wrong frame.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7686c8412e142a77384226d62aea8f0ab8a7ac2edbff4d307721c2bb3e6d9ce3",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1251
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "M C P isn't dying \u2014 it's getting demoted from the runtime to a primitive the runtime composes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bbd5e6b2cdbbcb62ef8a7adce18bbca9f70ef5e74bd7220bfdd5d8321761af2f",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 8.266303854875284,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1265
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "Bash for binaries. Typed imports for proprietary APIs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8b4f1da25745d4625180521c08b7e30b3256e321dc810f2b5b855d6101cd2071",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1283
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "M C P underneath when you need contracts and auth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f3e7fb05fce659f61a109dfbab5940861f8c6927fc474894120d0e2f22a2c96e",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1291
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "The agent picks per task. That's the answer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e90fdb27e916e2e504a5002e1338e510193e71ad81b040d6a35b01d777be176",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1301
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "Tell me in the comments which primitive you reach for first, and what's breaking your context window today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:292a7526d7614dd358b7bcc75ea4eea588a40c8262a94224552206d1f7c4e43a",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1309
    }
  ]
}